+----------------+
|Game Description|
+----------------+

A fortune in gold has been stolen and you've been hired to find and return it before the trail goes cold and it's lost forever. Seek &amp; find more than 2,100 hidden objects in 25 amazing San Francisco locations - from Alcatraz to the Golden Gate Bridge, Haight-Ashbury and Fisherman's Wharf - and track down the stolen gold! You are the world-famous Mystery P.I. and you have just 17 hours to piece together the clues hidden in the Golden Gate city. If you find the gold in time, you'll collect a handsome $20 million reward for your efforts. Are you up to the job?

Originally released September 15th, 2010.

+----------------------------------+
|Instructions / System Requirements|
+----------------------------------+

No install or crack is required for this portable version. Extract the ZIP file and create a shortcut to the executable (EXE) to play.

This game is compatible with Windows XP, Vista(32/64bit) and 7(32/64bit). Requires DirectX 7.0 or later. Processor requirements: 350MHz CPU or higher. RAM requirements: 128 MB or higher. Requires a DirectX-compatible Sound and Video card with at least 16 MB of video memory.

